# Produces: assets/launch/cli-blame-line.png

Output assets/launch/cli-blame-line.png

Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 860
Set Height 300
Set Padding 24
Set Shell "/tmp/vhs-shell.sh"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set WaitTimeout 15s

Sleep 500ms
Type "ghostshift blame auth.ts --line 1"
Enter
Sleep 2s
